Aggregation and Grouping Data

> 📺 Watch this episode: [YouTube Link]

 📌 What You Will Learn

- COUNT — count rows and non-null values
- SUM — add up numeric column values
- AVG — calculate average (with ROUND)
- MAX & MIN — highest and lowest values
- GROUP BY — aggregate results per group
- HAVING — filter groups after aggregation
- WHERE vs HAVING — when to use which

